               <head>A collection of mathematical and philosophocal works</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh2008107563   lccn.loc.gov/sh2008109238" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>A collection of mathematical and philosophocal works. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh2008107563">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1v" to="67r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Bar noten ṭa῾am</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">בר נותן טעם</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The work is divided into two parts. The first part consists of six chapter, the second part of three sections. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en">Kafanton, Jacob ben Isaac</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he">קפנטון, יעקב בן יצחק</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh2008109238">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="67v" to="182v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush ῾al ha-be᾿ur ha-emtsa῾i</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">פרוש על הבאור האמצעי </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A commentary on Averroes' intermediate commentary on Aristotle's Physics, based on the translation of Kalonymos ben Kalonymos. Prefixed are four separate notes. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The first chapter begins on folio 68r, the second on folio 81v, the third on folio 90v, the fourth on folio 101v, the fifth on folio 123r, the sixth on folio 132r, the seventh on folio 147r, and the eighth on folio 158r. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
